text: Helmut Wollmann (born 16 March 1947) is a German rower who represented East Germany. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics in Mexico City with the men's coxed pair where they came fourth. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of East Germany Category:Rowers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Berlin
